entities.name: Arbitrum DAO

entities.name: Claude

entities.name: Stan
entities.description: A developer or contributor actively involved in fixing critical security vulnerabilities, plugin issues (plugin-sql, plugin-twitter), and managing code repositories for ElizaOS.

entities.name: Shaw
entities.description: A contributor involved in deploying testnets, managing cross-chain liquidity pools, and performing cleanup work on code repositories for ElizaOS.

entities.name: OP
